                                            "type": "text",
                                            "content": "Figure 2: The overview of the pipeline in each iteration of BoT. To show how boosting is achieved in this experience-driven iteration process, we present detailed intermediate results obtained from an experiment on ChapGPT-4 on the Game of 24 dataset. Given "
