                                                2106,
                                                1590
                                            ],
                                            "type": "text",
                                            "content": " as input, The Thought Structures Generation (Stage 1) outputs massive heterogeneous tree thought structures. Thought Structures Aggregation (Stage 2) aggregated them into a thought chain "
                                        },
                                        {
                                            "bbox": [
                                                443,
                                                1339,
                                                2106,
                                                1590
                                            ],
                                            "type": "inline_equation",
