                                        2106,
                                        1894
                                    ],
                                    "type": "text",
                                    "content": "Instead of pre- preparing examples in the prompt, a more adaptive way is to design prompts to guide the LLMs to gradually generate the thought "
                                },
                                {
                                    "bbox": [
                                        443,
                                        1623,
                                        2106,
                                        1894
                                    ],
                                    "type": "inline_equation",
                                    "content": "z_{i}"
                                },
                                {
                                    "bbox": [
                                        443,
                                        1623,
                                        2106,
                                        1894
                                    ],
                                    "type": "text",
                                    "content": " during the reasoning process. This can be formalized as "
                                },
                                {
                                    "bbox": [
                                        443,
                                        1623,
                                        2106,
                                        1894
                                    ],
                                    "type": "inline_equation",
                                    "content": "z_{i} \\sim p_{0}\\left(z_{i} \\mathbb{I}\\left(z_{1\\ldots i - 1}, X, Q\\right)\\right)"
                                },
                                {
                                    "bbox": [
                                        443,
                                        1623,
                                        2106,
                                        1894
                                    ],
                                    "type": "text",
                                    "content": ". Finally, the solution is formalized as "
                                },
                                {
                                    "bbox": [
                                        443,
                                        1623,
                                        2106,
                                        1894
                                    ],
                                    "type": "inline_equation",
                                    "content": "y \\sim p_{\\theta}\\left(y \\mathbb{I}\\left(z_{1\\ldots n}, X, Q\\right)\\right)"
                                },
                                {
                                    "bbox": [
                                        443,
                                        1623,
                                        2106,
                                        1894
                                    ],
                                    "type": "text",
                                    "content": ". The representative approach, ToT Yao et al. (2024), further extends this sequential reasoning steps into a tree structure in which "
                                },
