                                        2636,
                                        2106,
                                        3049
                                    ],
                                    "type": "text",
                                    "content": "We propose Boosting of Thoughts (BoT), an automated prompting framework incorporating, which achieves prompt boosting with an experience- driven iteration process commencing with a simple prompt. As summarized in Fig. 2, each iteration "
                                },
                                {
                                    "bbox": [
                                        443,
                                        2636,
                                        2106,
                                        3049
                                    ],
                                    "type": "inline_equation",
                                    "content": "t"
                                },
                                {
                                    "bbox": [
                                        443,
                                        2636,
                                        2106,
                                        3049
                                    ],
                                    "type": "text",
                                    "content": " of BoT includes three stages. The Thought Structures Generation stage is able to fully explore reasoning chains generated by LLMs with the input prompt "
                                },
                                {
                                    "bbox": [
                                        443,
                                        2636,
                                        2106,
                                        3049
                                    ],
                                    "type": "inline_equation",
                                    "content": "\\mathbb{I}^t"
                                },
                                {
                                    "bbox": [
                                        443,
                                        2636,
                                        2106,
                                        3049
                                    ],
                                    "type": "text",
                                    "content": ". In the second stage, these thought structures are aggregated to form a reasoning chain, which is to be analyzed by LLMs in the third stage to produce feedback containing error reports and detailed revision advice. Combining the aggregated reasoning chain with the feedback results in a new experience, denoted as "
                                },
                                {
                                    "bbox": [
                                        443,
                                        2636,
                                        2106,
                                        3049
                                    ],
                                    "type": "inline_equation",
                                    "content": "\\mathbf{F}^t"
                                },
                                {
                                    "bbox": [
                                        443,
                                        2636,
                                        2106,
                                        3049
                                    ],
                                    "type": "text",
                                    "content": ". Thus, the prompt is enhanced by accumulating these experiences "
                                },
                                {
                                    "bbox": [
                                        443,
                                        2636,
                                        2106,
                                        3049
                                    ],
                                    "type": "inline_equation",
                                    "content": "\\mathbf{F}^{1\\ldots t}"
                                },
                                {
                                    "bbox": [
